ZH: 我们需要记住重要的日子，比如生日和结婚纪念日。
EN: We need to remember important dates, such as birthdays and anniversaries.

ZH: 在学习新词汇时，记住它们的拼音是很重要的。
EN: When learning new vocabulary, it is important to remember their pinyin.

ZH: 我会记住你为我做的一切，永远感激不尽。
EN: I will remember everything you have done for me and forever be grateful.

ZH: 记住，每个挑战都是一个成长的机会。
EN: Remember, every challenge is an opportunity for growth.

