EN: Consistency in exercising is the key to maintaining good health, remember that.

ZH: 请记住，让我们的行为与我们的价值观保持一致。
EN: Please remember to align our actions with our values.

ZH: 记住要尊重他人的意见，即使你不同意。
EN: Remember to respect others' opinions, even if you disagree.

